    <name>Cardboard</name>
    <summary>Browse art on boorus</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Cardboard can be used to browse different boorus, download posts, and also keep a local favorites collection across all of them, while also supporting adding individual links for some services and files</p>
        <p>Some features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Adaptive UI and post color theming</li>
          <li>AI autotag (uses Danbooru)</li>
          <li>Search autocomplete (uses Danbooru)</li>
          <li>Editing posts locally and viewing information about them</li>
          <li>Download posts</li>
          <li>Bookmark and blacklist tags</li>
          <li>Drop a file to add it to favorites</li>
          <li>Tabs and middle click to open tag/post in a new tab</li>
          <li>Restore tabs on start</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
